[[TUTO:Conditional execution]]
[[In REDACTED we have the venerable if, with the structure if <cond> then <expr> else <expr>]]
print '1 is' (if 1 then 'truthy' else 'falsy').
print '0 is' (if 0 then 'truthy' else 'falsy').

[[The else is optional]]
if 1 then print 'This will be printed'.
if 0 then print 'This will not be printed'.

[[If we want multiple statements we can choose]]
if 0 then
do
    'My statement'.
    'My statement'.
    '...'
done.

[[or...]]
if 0 then
(
    'My statement'.
    'My statement'.
    '...'
).
